Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
The Bottle Store is committed to protecting your privacy and will never, under any circumstances, disclose your information to a third party. Please read the following privacy policy which explains how we use and protect your information.
By visiting and/or ordering services on this app, you agree and, where required, you consent to the collection, use and transfer of your information as set out in this policy.
The information we collect about you, including your name, address, telephone number and email address will only be used to process your order and provide you with the best possible service. We may also collect information about your usage of the app, technical device information (e.g. device type, operating system, IP address, usage date & times) and use this information to enhance and personalize your experience.
Your information will enable us to provide you with access to the relevant parts of the app and to supply the services you have requested. It will also enable us to bill you and to contact you where necessary concerning our services. We will also use and analyse the information we collect so that we can administer, support, improve and develop our business, for any other purpose whether statistical or analytical and to help us prevent fraud.
The Bottle Store will not send you any emails other than those related to your order without your prior consent as provided by registering on our website and selecting the relevant checkbox. All electronic communications will include an easy option to 'unsubscribe'. Where you have chosen at a device level to begin or continue receiving push notifications from us, we may send you push notifications relating to the services that you have requested from us and information about our services and offers. You can choose to stop receiving push notifications from us at any time by changing your preferences on your mobile device or by contacting us at
customerservice
@thebottlestore.ae.
If you do not want us to use your data in this way or change your mind about being contacted in the future, please let us know by using the aforementioned contact details and/or amending your profile accordingly.
The Bottle Store take security extremely seriously. We employ the latest industry-standard security and encryption techniques and technologies to ensure your details are always kept safe and private.
We strongly advise that you keep your username and password secret at all times. If you have reasons to believe that somebody may have found out your password, change it immediately and notify us at
customerservice
@thebottlestore.ae so we can suspend your account.
All content of this app is Copyright ©The Bottle Store 2023. All rights reserved.
This app is for your personal, non-commercial use. You may not modify, copy, distribute, transmit, display, perform, reproduce, publish, license, create derivative works from, transfer, or sell any information, software, products or services obtained from this app. The Bottle Store and any other product or trade names of The Bottle Store referenced herein are our service marks or registered service marks. Other product and company names mentioned herein may be the trademarks of their respective owners.
Images, trademarks and brands displayed on this website are protected by copyright, trade mark and other intellectual property laws and may not be reproduced or appropriated in any manner without the written permission of their respective owner(s).
If you have any questions concerning legalities please send an email to
customerservice
@thebottlestore.ae and The Bottle Store will be happy to try and help you out wherever possible.
Any changes to our privacy policy will be posted to the Website and, where appropriate, through e-mail notification.
